Educational Use Notice:

This project is created primarily for educational purposes to demonstrate
Data Structures and Algorithms in a practical game development context.

Students, educators, and learners are encouraged to:
- Study the code
- Modify and extend the project
- Use it in coursework and assignments
- Share it with others for educational purposes

Dependencies:

This project uses the following external libraries:
- SFML (Simple and Fast Multimedia Library) - zlib/png license
- TGUI (Texus' Graphical User Interface) - zlib license

Please ensure compliance with their respective licenses when distributing
any modified versions of this software.

Asset Note:

The project structure includes placeholder directories for game assets
(graphics, sounds, fonts). Any assets you add to these directories may
have their own separate licenses. Ensure you have the right to use and
distribute any assets you include.
